<div class="container">
{{we-sys-messages messages=messages}}
{{partial 'partials/auth-navbar'}}
<form role="form" class="auth-form user-signup-form"  action="/login" method="post">

  <div class="form-content">

    <div class="user-signup-logo-cdp">
      {{partial 'partials/cdp-logo-svg'}}
    </div>
    <h2 class="form-heading">{{t "auth.login.title"}}</h2>
    <p style="margin: 20px 0;">A CdP migrou para outro servidor, por isso precisa que você recadastre a sua senha. Se você já fez esse procedimento, pode seguir adiante normalmente. Caso ainda não tenha feito clique <a href="/auth/forgot-password">aqui</a>.</p>
    <!-- input: email -->
    <div class="form-group">
      <div class="input-group">
        <input class="form-control input-lg" placeholder="Email" required="true" type="email" name="email">
        <label for="email" class="input-group-addon">
          <span class="icons-outline icons-outline-letter"></span>
        </label>
      </div>
    </div>


    <!-- input: password -->
    <div class="form-group">
      <div class="input-group">
        <input class="form-control input-lg" placeholder="Senha" required="true" type="password" name="password">
        <label for="password" class="input-group-addon">
          <span class="icons-outline icons-outline-padlock-closed"> </span>
        </label>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="form-group clearfix">
      <div class="input-group pull-right">
        <button class="btn btn-lg btn-success submit" type="submit">
          {{t "Send"}}
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align: center;">
      {{#link-to "authRegister"}}
        {{t "Sign up"}}
      {{/link-to}}
    </div>

    <input class="eu-gosto-de-mel" type="text" name="mel" value="" style="display: none">

  </div>
  <div class="form-footer">
    <ul>
      <li>
        {{#link-to "authForgotPassword"}}
          {{t "Remember Password"}}
        {{/link-to}}
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</form>
</div>